# qodana-ruby — Qodana for Ruby/RubyMine (image name = repoName), the PRIMARY ruby variant (RUBY 3.3,
# the default tag). Feed code QDRUBY, an EAP linter — the feed has NO `release` entries (all releases
# are Type=eap), so this is the fleet's FIRST eap image: QD_RELEASE_TYPE=eap (consumed only by the
# drift bumper to pick the newest EAP within the major; provision-dist uses the verbatim QD_VERSION/
# QD_BUILD). PUBLIC feed: OMITS QD_DISTRIBUTION_FEED. Builds on the DHI ruby language base (ruby PRE-
# BAKED, but NO node), so — like qodana-go/php — it LAYERS the node toolchain (NODE_MAJOR) + the in-
# place eslint pin for JS/TS support, plus the in-place lib/toolchain/ruby.dockerfile gem-cache
# redirect. Ruby scans shell out to sudo to install project gems (source PRIVILEGED=true), so it
# INCLUDEs lib/privileged.dockerfile. DIST_BASE_STAGE=privileged is an .env KEY (base.dockerfile does
# NOT default DIST_BASE_STAGE, so the INCLUDE_ARGS value survives to `FROM ${DIST_BASE_STAGE:-base} AS
# dist` — the android/php convention) so the dist layers onto privileged; PRIVILEGED_BASE_STAGE=base is
# a COMPOSE BUILD ARG (base.dockerfile defaults it to clang-toolchain, which would clobber an .env
# value, so it must be --build-arg to win — the cdnet convention) so privileged FROMs base (the
# in-place node+eslint+ruby toolchains). All 3 ruby variants share this SAME RM dist (QD_LINTER_SLUG=
# qodana-ruby — the IDE dist is ruby-runtime-agnostic, the android precedent) and differ ONLY in
# QD_BASE_IMAGE. uid 1000 is FREE on the ruby base, so default 1000, NO uid keys (the source uses 1001,
# but lib/base creates the qodana user at the free 1000 — a documented divergence, phase-0). eslint is
# pinned in lib/toolchain/eslint/package.json (renovate). Pins live in docs/phase-0-decisions.md;
# EnvContractTest asserts byte-identity for the dist pins + the 3.3 base digest. Key set = jvm's key set
# + DIST_BASE_STAGE (the php shape minus COMPOSER_IMAGE).
QD_LINTER_SLUG=qodana-ruby
QD_VERSION=2026.1
QD_BUILD=261.25886
QD_RELEASE_TYPE=eap
QD_PRODUCT_INFO_CODE=RM
QD_BASE_IMAGE=dhi.io/ruby:3.3-debian13-dev@sha256:207bdd81b3fbec45e858f7255a0e4032cd6c6bfa4c1348532c2c50989e361a73
DIST_BASE_STAGE=privileged
CLI_BINARY=qodana
CLI_VERSION=2026.2
CLI_OS=linux
NODE_MAJOR=20
